The '''Dusk Rose''' is a type of vegetation that exists in the region of [[Slaver's Bay]] on the continent of [[Essos]].

Dusk Rose tea eases fever, and is a commonly known local remedy around [[Meereen]] - particularly for the slaves who have to make the tea.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Two Swords]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
